    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Attack
    The Attack class holds information about the Pokemon's attack.
    Card
    The Card class holds information about the card that is in the deck.
    Charmander
    The Charmander class holds information about the pokemon Charmander for a Pokemon TCG game.
    Cynthia
    The Cynthia class is a trainer card that can be used in a Pokemon TCG game.
    Deck
    The Deck class holds the cards used in the game and holds methods that relate to the deck.
    Eevee
    The Eevee class holds information about the pokemon Eevee for a Pokemon TCG game.
    Electric
    The Electric class is an Electric Energy card.
    Energy
    The Energy class represents an energy card in the Pokemon TCG game.
    Fire
    The Fire class is a Fire Energy card.
    Lapras
    The Lapras class holds information about the pokemon Lapras for a Pokemon TCG game.
    Pikachu
    The Pikachu class holds information about the pokemon Pikachu for a Pokemon TCG game.
    Player
    The Player class handles the state of the player and contains methods to run the player's turn.
    PokeBall
    The PokeBall class is a trainer card that can be used in a Pokemon TCG game.
    Pokemon
    The Pokemon class holds information about a Pokemon including core stats about them.
    PokemonCardGame
    The PokemonCardGame class is responsible for creating and running a Pokemon TCG game between two players.
    PokemonCardGameTester
    The PokemonProjectTester class is responsible for testing the PokemonCardGame class and all related classes.
    ProfsLetter
    The ProfsLetter class is a trainer card that can be used in a Pokemon TCG game.
    ProfsResearch
    The ProfsResearch class is a trainer card that can be used in a Pokemon TCG game.
    RareCandy
    The RareCandy class is a trainer card that can be used in a Pokemon TCG game.
    Skarmory
    The Skarmory class holds information about the pokemon Skarmory for a Pokemon TCG game.
    Steel
    The Steel class is a Steel Energy card.
    Trainer
    The Trainer class holds information about trainer cards for a Pokemon TCG game.
    Water
    The Water class is a Water Energy card.
    XSpeed
    The XSpeed class is a trainer card that can be used in a Pokemon TCG game.
